4 ybe ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls22 ws0">无离合，因缘聚合定现前。<span class="_ _8"></span><span class="ls38">”意思是说，当金翅鸟翱翔在高</span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 ybf ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">空中时，<span class="_ _4"></span>它的影子暂时看不见，<span class="_ _6"></span>但是并非没有影子，<span class="_ _4"></span>最后无</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yc0 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">论它降落在哪里，<span class="_ _4"></span>黑乎乎的身影就会出现在此处。<span class="_ _6"></span>同样，<span class="_ _4"></span>今</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yc1 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">天你所造的任何恶业，<span class="_ _4"></span>虽不一定立竿见影、<span class="_ _6"></span>马上受报，<span class="_ _4"></span>但是</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yc2 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">到了来世，<span class="_ _d"></span>乃至来世的来世，<span class="_ _d"></span><span class="ls25">苦果不可能不降临到你的头上。<span class="_ _8"></span><span class="ls0"> </span></span></div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
